        "subject": "LU-1032 build: Remove include of lustre-version.ac",
        "message": "LU-1032 build: Remove include of lustre-version.ac\n\nThis is an experimental patch. It renames the lustre-version.ac file to\nlustre-version.m4. Also, it creates an m4 macro which is used to setup\nthe Lustre version variables which is called from configure.ac.\n\nChances are, cleanup like this will be needed to properly support DKMS\nbuilds. This patch is probably incomplete and/or incorrect in and of\nitself, but is meant to demonstrate the type of cleanup the build system\nmight needs to move forward.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly\nSigned-off-by: Prakash Surya <surya1@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: I4890a5718755362d9c2e122ddf02e47777896c64\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
